{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["After the Rain Comes the Sun\n\n<size=45>Chapter 6 - Rain Shower<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Fwahhh... I'm all wet now... Milord, here's a towel for you!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Yamashiro handed me a dry towel while drying her hair with her own towel.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Fusou always told me to come prepared in case it suddenly started raining. I guess it came in handy today...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Umm... something to change into, something to change into... Here it is! Give me just a-","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Uuu... Milord, you're also here... I-I'm sorry...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Turn around without saying anything"},{"flag":2,"content":"Head for the door"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Milord? It's still raining outside!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Um, umm... C-come back here, it's fine, really...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"All right, Milord! You can turn around now!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Sorry, I only have enough clothes for myself... but there are still fresh towels...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It's a shame that I couldn't finish my dance, though...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I sat next to Yamashiro and quietly ruffled her hair","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ehehe... why does it mean so much to me? Mm, I suppose I haven't told you before?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The first reason is that I want to ease some of my sister's burdens and responsibilities. The second reason is because, well, you know how Fusou and I have bad luck? Akashi said that it might be because people call us \"unlucky ships.\"","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But I think that... as ships, even if we had an unlucky service history, we can't forget about the lives and effort of the people involved...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"So, we should work hard to become happy and fortunate, to repay all those people for giving us this life...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:79}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":305020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"And with that, the rain began to pass.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"SHANCHENGP6","fadeOut":1.5}